OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fa single common law in     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FIndia                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, When it comes to matters such as       
OL,6, marriage, divorce, inheritance and     
OL,7, adoption, India has different laws for 
OL,8, different communities based on their   
OL,9, religion, faith and beliefs.           
OL,11,FBut since Independence there's been    
OL,12,Ftalk of an Uniform Civil Code or UCC, a
OL,13,Fsingle personal law for all citizens   
OL,14,Firrespective of religion, sex, gender  
OL,15,Fand sexual orientation. Even the       
OL,16,Fconstitution says the state should     
OL,17,F"endeavour" to provide such a law to   
OL,18,Fits citizens.                          
